Improve code quality
commitResults.messageBody:
Code quality could be improved. Method and variable names could be
more descriptive. Long methods could be extracted out of.

By improving quality of code, readers will not find it hard to
understand the code.

Let's,
* rename methods
* extract methods out of long methods in Parser and TaskList
  classes
* move method from TaskList to Storage classes

Methods will be much more descriptive for the reader. Extracting
from long methods will allow for much more readability.
Method was moved in consideration of better heeding the OOP
paradigm.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add use of assertions
commitResults.messageBody:
Assertions help to check if important assumptions hold at certain
points of the code. This ensures that the program will terminate
before any unintended consequence.

Let's add assertions into the code where important assumptions
were made.

So that important assumptions are holding.
